summary: Post-graduate economist with experience designing, delivering and managing projects that catalyse social and economic change. Has a diverse skillset that covers research and analysis for public policy, economic forecasting and modelling, public financial management and institutional strengthening. In addition to working with clients in the UK, has worked in Azerbaijan, Ethiopia, Papua New Guinea, Romania, and Tajikistan. Holds an MSc in Finance and Development from SOAS, University of London.
